<figureCitation box="[392,470,1685,1708]" captionStart="FIGURES 12, 13" captionStartId="4.[151,269,1942,1966]" captionText="FIGURES 12, 13. Wing of Betysyrphus keiseri sp. n., Photo of wing with diffuse darkened patch (Fig. 12) and schematic drawing of mictotrichia coverage and pile on lower calypter (Fig. 13)." pageId="6" pageNumber="46">
Fig. 
